---
import { BMC_URL } from "../data/links";
---

<section
  class="bg-cream py-16 sm:py-20"
  aria-labelledby="support-heading"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 text-center">
    <h2
      id="support-heading"
      class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-navy-deep sm:text-4xl"
    >
      Buy me a coffee
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink">
      Snap311 is free and I plan to keep it that way. If it's saved you a
      frustrating round-trip with the official app, a coffee covers Apple
      Developer fees and the next round of features.
    </p>

    <a
      href={BMC_URL}
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-navy px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-md transition hover:bg-navy-deep"
    >
      <span aria-hidden="true">☕</span> Buy Me a Coffee
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
